CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper February 8, 1947, pg. 17, reads: "Another Junior Party - Another junior set party last week was the birthday fete for little Miss Sandra Kay Anderson who is now five, at the home of her grandmother, Mrs. Edna Anderson of Wylie Avenue. The little folk really know how to get together and 'let the good times roll' when another year rolls around. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Sandra Kay Anderson surrounded by children for her fifth birthday party, in home of Edna Anderson with striped sofa, violin-shaped vases, and portrait photographs
